Name: Excise Tax, Beer and Liquor
Title: A Local Law in  relation to repeal subchapter 5 of chapter 20 of title 11 of the administrative code of the City of New York, in relation to the imposition of an excise tax on beer and liquor.
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

	Section 1. Subchapter 5 of chapter 20 of title 11 of the administrative code of the city of New York is REPEALED.
	ï¿½2. This local law shall take effect immediately.
